select * from `loans` order by `created_at` desc limit 5
select * from `loans` where `status` = 'approved' and date(`loan_date`) < '2025-06-08' and not exists (select * from `return_items` where `loans`.`id` = `return_items`.`loan_id`)
select `users`.*, (select count(*) from `loans` where `users`.`id` = `loans`.`user_id`) as `loans_count` from `users` order by `loans_count` desc limit 5

select `name`, SUM(loan_items.quantity) as total_borrowed from `items` inner join `loan_items` on `items`.`id` = `loan_items`.`item_id` group by `items`.`id`, `items`.`name` order by `total_borrowed` desc limit 5
